{"tid":1840450,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[蓄意播毒］武漢女高調發文「山東沒有病毒，所以我來了」. 隔天一家三口全被抓走","createTime":"2020-01-24T22:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T06:22:44.000Z","uid":226548,"like":695,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":133,"replies":[{"pid":"ef62f840baba386f499488fea1ac611432f6d782","tid":1840450,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://padforum.cc/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/F4ACFB5A-BEBD-4F20-A9F6-4D5575B01438-e1579882073627.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpadforum.cc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2FF4ACFB5A-BEBD-4F20-A9F6-4D5575B01438-e1579882073627.jpeg&h=4a5e308f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在武漢肺炎持續擴散下，湖北武漢市昨日（23日）早上10時起「封城」，封城前更引發了一陣「逃亡潮」。不少武漢網民紛紛在網上分享逃亡「心得」，有人更聲稱自己發燒，但仍要到上海廸士尼樂園遊玩。而一名武漢女子與丈夫攜同女兒一家三口<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逃到山東夫家準備過年，但她竟然高調地在微博發文稱「山東沒病毒 &hellip; 所以我來了」</span></strong>，還附上GPS位置地圖，公開透露自己在高青縣。結果網民瘋狂地向山東高青縣警方舉報，結果隔天一家三口都被警方捉去進行防控措施，真係大快人心。<br />\n<br />\n根據「高青警方」通報，一名微博女網友「瑾兒Sisisi運」22日發文表示，「大山東木（沒）有病毒&sdot;&sdot;&sdot;&sdot;&sdot;&sdot; 所以我來了」，並且放上自己的自拍照，發文地點註明在山東省淄博市高青縣。"},{"pid":"c695ce717761826fdf521390eaa7a103c65e6044","tid":1840450,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44b2092c4cd1696e7b06d9ebb81ec5e69b7b798","tid":1840450,"uid":191762,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為中國人團結？"},{"pid":"4c76a8a55cb14c5154aad2504fde49bb52b63a2e","tid":1840450,"uid":326897,"like":297,"dislike":7,"score":290,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:50:32.000Z","msg":"智障係硬傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係恭喜晒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753b69a83411c08935a81c5b0f0ab79d20baf938","tid":1840450,"uid"